		<RichText x="9" y="957" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">正常</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="6" y="1009" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="18" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="52" height="44" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="18" color="#ffffff">深渊大招后</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">鳞蜥进行右咬、左咬、下扑至多3段的普攻，依次造成<span color="#ffe599">40%,50%,65%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">鳞蜥凝聚力量，用凝晶的尾部发射岩流，造成<span color="#ffe599">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="425" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">开局或瘫痪恢复后施放，鳞蜥为自身附上<span color="#ffdfbf">晖岩之护</span><span>，岩抗提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">60%</span><span>；展开半径</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25m</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">蕴光领域</span><span>；清除前台角色的「蕴光之茧」时，晖岩之护将被立即破坏。<br/>施放「行虚空荡」之前，全队的「蕴光之茧」会被移除(仅移除，无增益)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_16.png')" x="719" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#937122" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#937122">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离太近或处于后方时，鳞蜥迅速自转扫尾，造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">鳞蜥在场地内促生多个岩蕨，每个造成<span color="#ffe599">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="441" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">鳞蜥移动到场地中央，展开穹顶，隐匿自身，并留下「<span textDecoration="underline">月锚岩</span><span>」；穹顶上有三只鳞蜥，其中一只会间歇性发射岩流，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">75%</span><span>伤害；25s后月锚岩爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">200%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
