		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_30.png')" x="576" y="726" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_31.png')" x="1248" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_32.png')" x="1248" y="438" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕴光月守宫.assets/Image_33.png')" x="1248" y="726" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="443" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">晖岩之护：鳞蜥展开蕴光领域时，<span color="#ffe599">岩元素</span><span>抗性</span><span color="#ffbfbf">+60%</span><span>，当角色清除前台角色的「蕴光之茧」时，晖岩之护将被立即破坏，并失去</span><span color="#ffe599">岩抗</span><span>提升。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="992" width="441" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蕴光之茧：暴击率<span color="#ffdfbf">-100%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-50%</span><span>，受治疗加成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-40%</span><span>；施加时，扣除全队角色</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%+1800</span><span>点生命值，若角色生命值低于</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7200</span><span>点，则改为扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35%</span><span>生命值，可致命但可开大招躲避；主动治疗清除后获得「出缠」效果。<br/>出缠：暴击率</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+15%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+50%</span><span>，持续15s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="960" width="434" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">月锚岩：<span color="#ffe599">2.8岩</span><span>盾，共9层，破坏后瘫痪7s；破坏第3/6/9层时会对鳞蜥造成</span><span color="#ffbfbf">6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">18%生命值</span><span>的伤害。<br/>(深境特化为</span><span color="#ffbfbf">4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffbfbf">12%生命值</span><span>)</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
</Graphic>